content.text:
- **Title:** Carrick Therapeutics Announces First Patient Dosed in Phase 1 Clinical Trial of CT7439 (CDK12/13 Inhibitor)  
  - **URL:** `https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2024/09/23/2951333/0/en/Carrick-Therapeutics-Announces-First-Patient-Dosed-in-Phase-1-Clinical-Trial-of-CT7439-CDK12-13-Inhibitor.html`  
  - **Direct quote snippets:**  
    - “CT7439, a novel cyclin dependent kinase 12/13 (CDK12/13) inhibitor / Cyclin-K glue-degrader.”  
    - “advanced solid tumors, including ovarian, breast and Ewing's Sarcoma.”  
    - “under study ID: NCT06600789.” ([globenewswire.com](https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2024/09/23/2951333/0/en/Carrick-Therapeutics-Announces-First-Patient-Dosed-in-Phase-1-Clinical-Trial-of-CT7439-CDK12-13-Inhibitor.html))

- **Title:** Trial | NCT06600789 (Clinical Drug Experience Knowledgebase / Purdue)  
  - **URL:** `https://cdek.pharmacy.purdue.edu/trial/NCT06600789/`  
  - **Direct quote snippets:**  
    - “A Modular Phase 1/2 Study With CT7439 in Participants With Solid Malignancies”  
    - “CT7439 Capsules (0.5 mg, 1mg, 3mg)”  
    - “Trial | NCT06600789” ([cdek.pharmacy.purdue.edu](https://cdek.pharmacy.purdue.edu/trial/NCT06600789/))

- **Title:** NCT06600789: An ongoing trial by Carrick Therapeutics Limited (FDAAA TrialsTracker)  
  - **URL:** `https://fdaaa.trialstracker.net/trial/NCT06600789/`  
  - **Direct quote snippets:**  
    - “NCT06600789: An ongoing trial by Carrick Therapeutics Limited”  
    - “Title  A Modular, Multi-Part, Multi-Arm, Phase 1/2 Study to Evaluate the Safety and Tolerability of CT7439 Alone” ([fdaaa.trialstracker.net](https://fdaaa.trialstracker.net/trial/NCT06600789/))

- **Title:** Non-enzymatic SETD1A activity drives breast cancer cell proliferation via cyclin K (Breast Cancer Research)  
  - **URL:** `https://breast-cancer-research.biomedcentral.com/articles/10.1186/s13058-025-02101-x`  
  - **Direct quote snippets:**  
    - “CT7439, a dual inhibitor of CDK12/13 and a cyclin K glue degrader,”  
    - “including breast cancer (NCT06600789).” ([breast-cancer-research.biomedcentral.com](https://breast-cancer-research.biomedcentral.com/articles/10.1186/s13058-025-02101-x))

- **Title:** CDK12/13 Inhibitor (Carrick Therapeutics pipeline page)  
  - **URL:** `https://www.carricktherapeutics.com/pipeline/cdk1213-inhibitor`  
  - **Direct quote snippets:**  
    - “CT7439: CDK12/13 inhibitor/Cyclin-K Degrader”  
    - “CT7439 is a CDK12/13/Cyclin-K degrader, which potently inhibits the cellular activity of CDK12/13.”  
    - “including breast, ovarian and Ewing's Sarcoma.” ([carricktherapeutics.com](https://www.carricktherapeutics.com/pipeline/cdk1213-inhibitor))

- **Title:** Carrick Therapeutics Announces First Patient Dosed in Phase 1 Clinical Trial of CT7439 (CDK12/13 Inhibitor) (BioSpace)  
  - **URL:** `https://www.biospace.com/press-releases/carrick-therapeutics-announces-first-patient-dosed-in-phase-1-clinical-trial-of-ct7439-cdk12-13-inhibitor`  
  - **Direct quote snippets:**  
    - “under study ID: NCT06600789.”  
    - “CT7439 is an inhibitor of CDK12/13 as well as a 'glue degrader' of Cyclin-K”  
    - “including ovarian, breast and Ewing's Sarcoma.” ([biospace.com](https://www.biospace.com/press-releases/carrick-therapeutics-announces-first-patient-dosed-in-phase-1-clinical-trial-of-ct7439-cdk12-13-inhibitor))
